<div dir="ltr"><br clear="all"><div><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Hey folks!</span></p>
<br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">We just released another beta version of Ushahidi v3. </span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"><font>What’s in it?</font></span></h2>
<br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">A sneak peek into some of the things to expect from this release include:-</span></p>
<br><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt">
<span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">New features like</span></p></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent">
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">A complete map configuration UI</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent">
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Searching for messages by sender name</span></p></li></ul><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent">
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">A security fix for the “Rosetta Flash” JSONP attack</span></p>
</li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Tags are no longer incorrectly referred to as &quot;categories&quot;</span></p>
</li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">The update script now has a non-developer &quot;deploy&quot; option</span></p>
</li></ul><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Have a look at </span><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/releases/tag/v3.0.0-beta.3" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">our release notes</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> and </span><a href="http://wp.me/p4vfAA-478" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">blog post announcement</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> for more details on changes in this release. </span></p>
<br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Take it out for a spin on our </span><a href="http://v3.ushahididev.com/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">demo site</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">, but keep in mind that this is still not quite ready for production yet ( we’re getting closer though). </span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"><font>What should I expect in the near future?</font></span></h2>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">We’re planning a series of user specific meetups in the coming weeks, focused on UI/UX pain points, as well as toolkit and user documentation. Stay tuned for updates on this. </span></p>
<br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">We also welcome feedback on any topics you would like to discuss.</span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"><font>How can you help?</font></span></h2>
<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt">
<span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Grab the code on </span><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/releases/tag/v3.0.0-beta.3" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">github</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">, or </span><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Ushahidi+3.x+Downloads" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">download it here</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">, then head over to the </span><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Installing+Ushahidi+3.x" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">install instructions</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">. </span></p>
</li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Setting+up+an+Ushahidi+3.x+development+build" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Set up a development build</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> and follow our </span><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Ushahidi+v3.x%2C+Development+process" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">developer processes</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> to send in bug reports and submit changes</span></p>
</li><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt">
<span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">If you’re not already set up on</span><a href="http://phabricator.org/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> Phabricator</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">, please head over to the </span><a href="https://phabricator.ushahidi.com/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Ushahidi Phabricator page </span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">and sign up. Once your account is approved, </span><a href="https://phabricator.ushahidi.com/w/help/phabricator/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">here’s a guide to get you started</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">.</span></p>
</li></ul><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Alternatively, just head over to the </span><a href="http://v3.ushahididev.com/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">demo site</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">, have a look and submit bug reports/share your thoughts/comments with us. </span></p>
</li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">You can also join our discussions on </span><a href="http://irc.lc/freenode/ushahidi" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">IRC</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">/Mailing list</span></p>
</li></ul><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"><font>v3 demo and Code Walkthrough</font></span></h2>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">This next week, we want to take sometime to give developers a live code walkthrough, to help you understand the structural changes and what to expect when jumping into coding on v3. Take advantage of the time you will have to pose questions to members of the team ;).</span></p>
<br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Join us on </span><a href="http://www.meetup.com/Ushahidi-Community/events/194155542/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">17th July, 2014 at 6.00p.m EAT | 8.00 a.m PDT | 11.00 a.m EST</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> (</span><a href="http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20140717T15" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">See timezone conversion information</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">)</span></p>
<br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">For those who missed last week’s demo and walkthrough,here is a </span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DoxKtpApmm0" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">link to the recording</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">.</span></p>
